---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro'
import LightRays from '@/components/light-rays'
---

<Layout fullDark>
    <div class="h-130 -z-5 absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2"><LightRays client:load raysColor="#00e17c" saturation={2} /></div>

    <header>
        <h1 class="text-lg text-center">Free Website Portfolio</h1>
        <h2 class="text-center text-muted-foreground">Open Call – 06/26</h2>
    </header>

    <main class="mt-15 space-y-13">
        <section>
            <h2 class="text-muted-foreground">Overview</h2>
            <div class="space-y-2">
                <p>An opportunity for one creative, independent professional, or small business to receive a <strong>custom website at no development cost</strong>.</p>
                <p>
                    The primary purpose of this initiative is to expand my public portfolio. While I've worked on a variety of real-world projects, many of them cannot be
                    showcased due to confidentiality. As I continue my job search, having more publicly accessible work helps better represent my experience and approach
                    to web development.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Rather than creating a fictional case study, I'd prefer to use this opportunity to support someone who could benefit from having a professional online
                    presence. The selected project will be treated like any other paid assignment.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2 class="text-muted-foreground">Result</h2>
            <div class="space-y-2">
                <p>The selected participant will receive a website with:</p>
                <ul class="list-['–'] list-inside">
                    <li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Home, About Me, and Work/Projects pages.</li>
                    <li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Responsive and customized design (not generic designs).</li>
                    <li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Contact and social media links.</li>
                    <li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;SEO, performance, and accessibility optimization.</li>
                    <li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;SSL certificate.</li>
                    <li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;A free <code>.vercel.app</code> domain.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>A custom domain is optional and may be purchased by the participant.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2 class="text-muted-foreground">Not Included</h2>
            <div class="space-y-2">
                <p>To keep the project manageable, the following are excluded:</p>
                <ul class="list-['–'] list-inside">
                    <li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Redesigns of existing portfolio websites.</li>
                    <li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;E-commerce functionality.</li>
                    <li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Complex web applications.</li>
                    <li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Large databases or CMS migrations.</li>
                    <li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Ongoing maintenance after delivery unless agreed separately.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2 class="text-muted-foreground">How to Apply</h2>
            <div class="space-y-2">
                <p>Participation is simple:</p>
                <ul class="list-['–'] list-inside">
                    <li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Send me a DM on Instagram introducing yourself, what you do, and why you'd like to be selected.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Following the account is appreciated, but it's not required. All applicants will receive a response indicating whether they were selected.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2 class="text-muted-foreground">Participant Responsibilities</h2>
            <div class="space-y-2">
                <p>The selected participant agrees to:</p>
                <ul class="list-['–'] list-inside">
                    <li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Provide required content (text, images, branding, etc.) in a timely manner.</li>
                    <li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Communicate during development.</li>
                    <li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Review deliverables and provide feedback when requested.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2 class="text-muted-foreground">Timeline</h2>
            <div class="space-y-2">
                <p>
                    The deadline for submitting applications is <strong>Friday, June 26, 2026</strong>. Following the selection process, the project schedule will be
                    agreed upon directly with the selected participant, based on the scope of the project and the participant's availability.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>
